The paper proposes a new graph generation technique for drug discovery, which involves the use of a hierarchical encoder-decoder model. The model is evaluated on multiple molecule generation tasks, including polymers. Given the focus on machine learning and deep learning techniques for graph generation, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). However, the paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques, as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
